      "role": "user",
      "content": "right, so if the main argument is that it's just protecting the big powers, doesn't that make the whole \"international law\" thing kind of a joke? like, if the rules only apply when the big guys want them to, is there actually any real legitimacy to the UN anymore, or is it just a mask for power politics?",
